  "title": "Trackwork Project Manager [Railway]/Up to $27k basic+bonus/Construction maincon",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Up to $27k basic salary.</strong></li><li><strong>Participating large-scale Trackwork and Rail projects.</strong></li><li><strong>The project is located in the central area.</strong></li><li><strong>Having experience in Railway or Trackwork project experience is mandatory.</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Our client, is a leading specialist in the Railway Industry currently inviting individuals onboard to join them in their latest venture.</strong></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Leading Project team from conceptual design to handing over to client.</li><li>Ensure the project meets the project schedule/ work program.</li><li>Ensure the project is in line with Health, Safety & Environmental requirements and local regulations.</li><li>Coordinate interface activities from testing, installation, and delivery.</li><li>Maintaining the highest standards in delivering the project following Client and stakeholders' (internally & externally) Policies & Procedures.</li><li>Managing and ensuring resources, manpower, materials, and contractors are in line with the project plan.</li><li>Ensure all contractual obligations are fulfilled and successfully performed according to the contract.<br />Ensuring and managing the Cost, Quality, and delivery of the project.<br />Ensuring that all works are reviewed regularly, identify and resolve issues if any.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Degree in Civil Engineering/Mechanical Engineering/ Electrical Engineering or equivalent.</li><li>Having experience in Railway or Trackwork project experience is mandatory.</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information:</strong></p><p><strong>To apply please click on APPLY NOW to submit your resume with the following details:</strong></p><ul><li>Reason for leaving each past & current employment</li><li>Salary drawn for each past & current employment</li><li>Expected Salary</li><li>Earliest availability date</li></ul><p><strong>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p><p><strong>Lionel Cheow</strong></p><p><strong>EA License | 14C7092</strong></p><p><strong>EA Registration Number | R1105005</strong></p>",
